Package: RadarOmics
Type: Package
Title: Visualise Omics Data Using Multidimensional Reduction and Radar Charts
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Emma", "Gairin", email = "emma.gairin@hotmail.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Dimensional reduction techniques (scaling, PCA, LDA) used to summarise expression profiles across large numbers of samples and treatments for targeted biological processes. Values representing expression profiles visualised with radar charts. Input from normalised gene expression tables or other datasets with similar structures (e.g., gene/protein as rows, samples as columns).
